ABOUT DATALYTICS

A Few Words About Us

Datalytics is a registered club of Coimbatore Institute of Technology, initiated for enlightening the knowledge of students in the field of data science. Our aim is to provide you:

  • Quality research & analysis
  • Business advisory experience
  • Realtime experience with data.
